org.apache.hadoop.fs.s3a

Class AWSCredentialProviderList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.fs.s3a.AWSCredentialProviderList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.amazonaws.auth.AWSCredentialsProvider

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
 @InterfaceStability.Evolving
public class AWSCredentialProviderList
extends Object
implements com.amazonaws.auth.AWSCredentialsProvider
    A list of providers. This is similar to the AWS SDK AWSCredentialsProviderChain, except that:
    1. Allows extra providers to be added dynamically.
    2. If any provider in the chain throws an exception other than an AmazonClientException, that is rethrown, rather than swallowed.
    3. Has some more diagnostics.
    4. On failure, the last AmazonClientException raised is rethrown.
    5. Special handling of AnonymousAWSCredentials.
